parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to shift harshly or not shift at all, leading to a loss of vehicle control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts hard
the vehicle won't shift at all
unusual noises or vibrations when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Angle gear failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of vehicle control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Leaking angle gear
unusual noises or vibrations from the transmission area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unusual transmission noises and vibrations can indicate a problem with the transmission, which can lead to a loss of vehicle control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded if left unaddressed.
symptoms: Whooping or crane-like sound when stepping on the accelerator and releasing
knocking noise coming from underneath the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster can lead to a loss of critical vehicle information, including speed, fuel level, and warning lights, which can compromise vehicle safety and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard and speedometer go blank
the SRS warning light is illuminated
the driver instrument module fails intermittently or completely
the instrument panel and dash lights flash on and off randomly
the vehicle's information system displays false warnings (e.g.
airbag problem).

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake lights can increase the risk of rear-end collisions, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intention to stop.
symptoms: The left and right side brake lights do not illuminate when the pedal is depressed
even after replacing the bulbs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to a failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The vehicle's information system displays a false warning of an airbag problem
even though the airbags have never been activated or deployed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates independently without warning
the engine RPM increases suddenly
the vehicle surges forward while the brake pedal is pressed
the vehicle accelerates at a high rate even when the transmission is in reverse gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt latch/catch can lead to the seat belt not connecting properly, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt will not connect
the seat belt catch assembly does not work
the seat belt latch/catch fails to operate correctly.
